high_descs: Turn right, move to the coffee machine on the counter, turn left to face the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn around and go to the microwave on the left.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter, then turn left to face the coffee machine.
Pick up the white mug from inside the coffee machine.
Turn around and turn left and walk toward the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave, heat it, and remove from the microwave.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then turn left to face the coffee machine.
Put the mug back into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the mug from the coffee machine.

high_descs: Go to the right and stand facing the coffee maker.
Pick the white cup up from under the coffee maker.
Turn to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the cup and shut the door.
Turn to the left and face the coffee maker.
Put the cup under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed cup under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Take a few steps to the right toward the coffee machine.
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee machine.
Carry the mug, and go to the microwave to the right side of the counter.
Place the mug inside the microwave and turn it on. Take the mug back out, and shut the door.
Hold the mug and turn left to go back to the coffee machine.
Place the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Warm a mug and place it on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right, go to counter, turn left to face coffee maker.
Pick up mug from coffee maker.
Turn around facing the wall, turn left to the microwave.
Open microwave door, put mug in on left side, close door, turn on.  Open door when done, take out the mug.
Turn left and go to the coffee maker.
Put mug on coffee maker, in the mug spot on the right hand side.
Turn right and walk a few feet over to the coffee maker on the counter
Pick up the white mug from the coffee maker
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the counter
Heat the mug in the microwave and remove it
Turn left and walk forward to the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the coffee maker
